for installing packages in python in ubuntu(linux) enter the following command into command window 
	sudo apt-get install python-numpy python-scipy python-matplotlib python-pandas python-sympy python-nose

To run a python .py file navigate to the file location in terminal by entering: cd home/workspace ...  
and run the scirpt by typing: python script.py
for WINDOWS 
